{"tid":396664,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【借錢梗要還】輝山乳業遭滙豐追討貸款及利息 限3日還錢","createTime":"2017-09-12T00:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T00:08:30.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9109cf264c16fa953232406ce28683b4ca7c8d","tid":396664,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170911/large/1505145197_4dcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170911%2Flarge%2F1505145197_4dcf.jpg&h=d7334d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n輝山乳業(6863)公布，於上周五(8日)及今日(11日)分別收到兩封來自滙豐的來函，指貸款協議的一項或以上違約事件經已發生並持續，所有貸款、應計利息及所有其他應計或尚未償清金額，已即時到期及應予償付，並須於3日內支付。<br />\n<br />\n據該來函所指，於今日美元批次的尚未清償本金額為1.8億美元(約14億港元)，而港元批次則為1.56億元，未繳付應計利息分別約576.71萬美元(約4498.35萬港元)及468.9萬元。<br />\n<br />\n同時，該公司亦收到另一封來自滙豐的來函，內容有關滙豐於2014年向該公司提供的另一筆銀行貸款，而滙豐已終止有關貸款，並要求即時償還總額1370.5萬美元(約1.07億港元)。<br />\n<br />\n輝山正聽取法律意見，並相信任何還款安排將連同償務重組建議一併考慮。公司會繼續與其中國主要銀行債權人，就其債務重組進行對話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57198245&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57198245%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170911&d=B095%2B7ONDbWzZWxw%2F2NrjzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9f486082\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57198245%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170911&h=eb48084e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57198245&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170911</a>"},{"pid":"4e40ec01c2a48d790d46dc77ca79e67e11a975ea","tid":396664,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:04:05.000Z","msg":"支那就快爆煲"},{"pid":"8d98f650e23e2b324c4b75ba75ffc6869cd0aee2","tid":396664,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:07:51.000Z","msg":"老千局爆左"},{"pid":"ff7212f6aee7fa7ed025ddd63f5feaaf3183e74d","tid":396664,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:08:30.000Z","msg":"還得到先好借"}]}